{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div data-lake-element=\"root\" class=\"lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-parser-by=\"lake2html\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">目前常用的 Linux 发行版主要包括 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">Debian/Ubuntu</code> 系列和 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">CentOS/Fedora</code> 系列。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">前者以自带软件包版本较新而出名；后者则宣称运行更稳定一些。选择哪个操作系统取决于读者的具体需求。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">使用 Docker，读者只需要一个命令就能快速获取一个 Linux 发行版镜像，这是以往包括各种虚拟化技术都难以实现的。这些镜像一般都很精简，但是可以支持完整 Linux 系统的大部分功能。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">本章将介绍如何使用 Docker 安装和使用 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">Busybox</code>、<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">Alphine</code>、<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">Debian/Ubuntu</code>、<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">CentOS/Fedora</code> 等操作系统。</p></div>",
